### Validierungsfehler – leerer Name (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/organisations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": ""
}

### Nicht gefundene Organisation (404)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/organisations/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Existiert nicht"
}

### Kein Token → 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/organisations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ohne Auth"
}
